trans-unit.source: The ToolboxItemCreator class encapsulates toolbox item creator callback functions.
trans-unit.target: Klassen ToolboxItemCreator innkapsler verktøykassen elementet creator tilbakeringing funksjoner.

trans-unit.source: These callback functions are used by designers to provide ways to create toolbox items for custom data objects.
trans-unit.target: Disse funksjonene tilbakeringing som brukes av utviklere måter å opprette verktøykassen elementer for egendefinert dataobjekter gi.
Oppretter en ny <xref href="System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem"> </xref> fra en <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.IDataObject"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The `data` parameter might contain data provided by the <xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItemContainer> class.
trans-unit.target: Den `data` parameter kan inneholde data i en <xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItemContainer>klasse.</xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItemContainer>

trans-unit.source: It might contain data that can be read by one of the <xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItemCreator> classes that have been supplied by the user.
trans-unit.target: Det kan inneholde data som kan leses av en av de <xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItemCreator>klasser som er oppgitt av brukeren.</xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItemCreator>

trans-unit.source: It might also be data with a Clipboard format that has a <xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItemCreator> assigned to it.
trans-unit.target: Det kan være data med et utklippstavleformat som har en <xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItemCreator>tilordnet.</xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItemCreator>

trans-unit.source: In this case, the <xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem> is created on demand.
The Create method might raise an exception if the data object does not contain data for the supported format.
trans-unit.target: Create-metoden kan vise et unntak hvis dataobjektet ikke inneholder data for format som støttes.

trans-unit.source: A data object that represents a <xref href="System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Et dataobjekt som representerer en <xref href="System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: A new instance of the <xref href="System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: En ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Gets the Clipboard format that represents the data needed to deserialize a <xref href="System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Henter utklippstavlen-format som representerer dataene som kreves for deserialisering av et <xref href="System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: When a drag-and-drop operation occurs, the design environment queries all <xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItemCreator> instances.
trans-unit.target: Når det oppstår en dra og slipp, utformingsmiljøet i spørringer alle <xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItemCreator>forekomster.</xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItemCreator>

trans-unit.source: If a <xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItemCreator> supports any of the dragged Clipboard formats, a <xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem> is created from the <xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItemCreator>.
trans-unit.target: Hvis en <xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItemCreator>støtter dratt utklippstavlen formater, en <xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem>opprettes fra <xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItemCreator>.</xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItemCreator> </xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem> </xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItemCreator>

trans-unit.source: A string representing the Clipboard format.
